  <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Why we exist</h2>
    <p class="lead">Because most Airbnb hosts don't have professional cleaning that is reliable and convenient for their Airbnb rental. Finding on demand professional cleaning is a hassle. Using TaskRabbit or asking a friend is unreliable. Cleaning yourself is okay, but it does not always work with your schedule and it takes time. And what if you have multiple guests coming while you are away?</p>
  </div>

