  <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">How it works</h2>
    <div class="lead">
      <p>You select a day and time when you need cleaning and tell us a little about your apartment. We will instantly let you know if we are available. You then choose exactly what you need and we quote you a price.</p>
      <p>Then all that's left is peace of mind... We clean your place and confirm promptly when the job is done. After the cleaning request is completed, payment is collected.</p>
      <p>Have questions or suggestions? We would be delighted to hear from you. Please <a href="/home#contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

