  <div class="featurette">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">What we offer</h2>
    <div class="lead">
      <p>We offer four different services</p>
      <ul type="disc">
        <li>We clean your home before your Airbnb guests arrive</li>
        <li>We prep your home before your guests arrive</li>
        <li>We prep your place between Airbnb guest stays</li>
        <li>We clean your place after Airbnb guests leave</li>
      </ul>
      <p>What is the difference between before cleaning and before prep? When you need someone to come in and really clean the place, we send in two professional for two hours. They do a full, thorough cleaning. When you simply need somone to come in and change the sheets put out clean towels, clear away any clutter in the house and make sure the bathroom is clean, we send someone in for an hour to "prep" your place. This is not a cleaning, we just make sure that your home is ready for guests.</p>
      <p>Likewise, our between guest stays prep is not a cleaning. We come in for an hour between when your first guests leave and your second guests arrive. We clean up any mess that was left by your first guests. We change the sheets and towels, take out the trash, clean the dishes, wipe down the countertops, make sure there is toilet paper in the bathrooms and generally ensure that your place is Airbnb ready for your next guests.</p>
      <p>After your guests leave we will do a post Airbnb cleaning. We send in our cleaning team to change your sheets and towels, take out the trash, sanitize the kitchen and bathrooms. Any messes made by your guests, we take care of it and make sure your home is ready for you when you return. This is not a "deep clean." However, if you want more than just a standard cleaning, please contact us and we will be happy to accommodate any of your particular requests.
    </div>
  </div>

