        <h5 id="services">What cleaning services do you provide?</h5>
        <p>Every clean comes with standard cleaning. We change the sheets and towels, wipe/vacuum the floors, take out the trash, clean any dishes and the kitchen sink and generally tidy up. We also offer a deep clean with additional services. For additional information see our <a href="/booking1">service list</a>. Our staff is very familiar with Airbnb and knows what is expected of Airbnb hosts. We will make sure that your place is ready for guests.</p>
        <h5 id="reliable">Are your cleaners reliable?</h5>
        <p>Absolutely. We understand that your reputation is on the line as a host, and we take that very seriously. We will show up on time and deliver excellent service. Concerns?  <a href="#contact">Call us</a>. We have your back and we truly care about your experience.</p>
        <h5 id="sheets">How do I return sheets and towels?</h5>
        <p>Just let us know when you are ready to return sheets and towels and we will pick them up within 24 hours.</p>
        <h5 id="insured">Are the cleaners bonded, insured and background checked?</h5>
        <p>Absolutely. We are bonded and insured and all of our cleaners have been vetted and thoroughly background checked.</p>
        <h5 id="payment">How do I pay?</h5>
        <p>After the cleaning is complete, we will send you an email with a link for accepting payment. We accept all major credit cards through Stripe.</p>
        <h5 id="present">Do I need to be home when the cleaners arrive?</h5>
        <p>Nope. Just let us know how to get in.</p>
        <h5 id="supplies">Do I need to provide cleaning supplies?</h5>
        <p>No. We come with our own environmentally friendly cleaning supplies. However, if you have supplies you would prefer we use, that is no problem.</p>
